The city of Palm Desert, Calif. and the SunLine

The city of Palm Desert, Calif. and the SunLine
Transit Agency in Thousand Palms have inaugurated
a zero-emission electric bus service. The
"Shopper Hopper" connects various Palm Desert
shopping districts. The Specialty Vehicle
Manufacturing Corporation bus employs lead-acid
batteries. SunLine, Dick Cromwell, 619-343-3456;
fax 619-343-1986.




