MITCHELL DIRECTORS DECLARE DIVIDENDS

Directors of Mitchell Energy & Development Corp. (NYSE: MND A,
MND B), The Woodlands, TX, have declared regular quarterly
cash dividends of 12 cents per share on the company's Class A
common stock and 13.25 cents per share on its Class B common
stock. The dividends are payable Jan. 4, 1996, to stockholders
of record at the close of business on Dec. 21, 1995.



<A HREF ="#HeadList">Back to Headline List</A><BR>
