        RPT     ASSMT. PERIOD   OPS     MNT     ENG     PL SP
        6/94    5/93-5/94       2       2       1       1
                                OPS     MNT     ENG     PL SP
        12/95   5/94-11/95      1       1       2       1

Copyright 1996 The McGraw-Hill Companies



