SHV CALOR EXPANDS IN BRAZIL

The international LPG joint venture of Calor Group of the UK and Dutch
SHV Energy is spending $62m for a 49% stake (with 50% voting rights) in
Supergasbras Distribuidora de Gas, Brazil's fourth largest LPG
