EL PASO BUYS PREMIER GAS

USA - El Paso Natural Gas has bought Premier Gas, which markets to
commercial and industrial gas users in the Mid-continent, as well as
utilities in the Great Lakes.

Last year's sales were 150 Bcf. Premier now becomes a unit of Eastex
energy, which has sales around 2 Bcfd.



