COPHILL PLUGGING WELL IN PHILIPPINES

Philippines - Cophill Exploration Corp was plugging its Dalingding-l
well in northern central Cebu Island having found only salt water and
small gas traces, the Philippines energy department said this week.
Total well depth was 1,508 ft.



