some extent on the rig selected.  With Norwegian rig availability very
tight, Hydro is keeping a close watch on the market and is maintaining
ongoing discussions with contractors to enable it to make a quick
decision when the right rig becomes available at the right price.

Norsk Hydro is also part of a consortium with Statoil and Saga awaiting
for the announcement of Norwegian 15th round licence awards before
proceeding with the fixture of a rig for a shared deepwater drilling
programme on the Voering Plateau starting end-1996 or early in 1997.

